author: Fearless & Far
description:
In just 72 hours, we went full Mongol warrior mode—deep in the wilds of Mongolia, in the dead of winter. We wrestled like ancient champions, feasted on boiled sheep head, downed fermented horse milk (yes, it’s intense), and trained in horseback archery on the open steppe. This is what it takes to live like a true Mongol warrior. Saddle up.

Want to do your own 4x4 Trip of Mongolia? Check out https://themongoliatour.com/.
